#####################################
## REQUIRED INPUT FILES/DIRECTORIES
#####################################

* fastq/ : put all fastq[.gz] files here (symbolic links are accepted as well)

* sample-sheet.tsv : tab-separated file with the following fields:
1. SAMPLE-NAME
2. GROUP-NAME(S)
3. FASTQ-R1-FILE(S)
4. FASTQ-R2-FILE(S)
5. GENOME (e.g. hg19, mm10)
6. ENZYME (e.g. HindIII, NcoI)


